text.text:
Tasty Iraqi BBQ in modest and unassuming restaurant.
Came to this restaurant from Google Maps, at first the restaurant doesn't look very convincing but don't let that fool you.
The BBQ is tasty and with right amount of spice. I also tried the sauted meat platter with tahini which was amazing. Will definitely come back next time.
